    {
      "id": "t_env_setup",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 90,
      "y": 90,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "🏗️  Environment Setup\n      Agent\n\nRuns: Once per AWS account\n\nSets up:\n• IAM roles, S3, KMS\n• Glue, LF-Tags, MWAA\n• MCP Gateway (optional)\n• Runtime (optional)",
