      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "r_env_setup",
      "originalText": "🏗️  Environment Setup\n      Agent\n\nRuns: Once per AWS account\n\nSets up:\n• IAM roles, S3, KMS\n• Glue, LF-Tags, MWAA\n• MCP Gateway (optional)\n• Runtime (optional)",
