      "originalText": "📊  Data Onboarding\n       Agent\n\nRuns: Per data source\n\nCreates:\n• Bronze→Silver→Gold\n• Glue jobs, DAG\n• Quality checks\n• Lake Formation tags\n• Spawns 4 sub-agents",
