      "height": 160,
      "text": "📈  Data Analysis\n       Agent\n\nRuns: On-demand\n\nCreates:\n• QuickSight dashboards\n• SQL queries\n• Semantic layer queries\n• Saves to SynoDB\n• Learns over time",
